short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: A Ravencoin wallet for Chrome browsers.

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: HoneyBlock's initial release allows sending of Ravencoin and Ravencoin assets, as well as tracking recent transactions. With browser messaging capabilities, HoneyBlock will soon power a new generation of connected sites for the Ravencoin blockchain!
